@startuml sd-01-register-issue-detailed
!include ../_shared/its-uml-style.puml

title Detailed SD 01 - Register Issue
hide footbox

actor "Auth User" as User
participant "issueController:IssueController" as IC
participant "issueService:IssueService" as IS
participant "targetProject:Project" as Project

User -> IC : registerIssue(title, description, priority)

alt not authorized
  IC --> User : permissionDenied()
else invalid title or description
  IC --> User : validationError(missingFields)
else valid and authorized
  note right of IC
  issueController는 UC1의 SSD system operation을 수신한다.
  Controller는 현재 사용자 확인 후 application service에 위임하고,
  권한 정책, 프로젝트 조회, 현재 시각, 영속성 처리는
  IssueService 협력으로 조정한다.
  end note

  IC -> IS : registerIssue(projectId, title, description,\npriority, currentUserId)
  activate IS

  IS -> Project : verify selected project exists\nand can receive issue
  activate Project
  Project --> IS : projectId
  deactivate Project

  create "newIssue:Issue" as Issue
  IS --> Issue : create(PersistedState(projectId, title,\ndescription, reporter)\n.priority(priority or MAJOR)\n.reportedDate(now))
  activate Issue

  create "createdHistory:IssueHistory" as CreatedHistory
  Issue --> CreatedHistory : new(action=CREATED,\npreviousValue=null,\nnewValue=NEW,\nchangedBy=currentUser,\nchangedDate=now)
  Issue -> Issue : addHistory(createdHistory)

  note right of Issue
  OC-01 사후조건:
  - Issue.status = NEW
  - reporter = currentUser
  - reportedDate = now
  - priority = priority 또는 MAJOR
  - IssueHistory(CREATED) 기록
  - changedBy=currentUser는
    User-IssueHistory changes association 형성을 의미
  end note

  Issue --> IS : createdWithHistory
  deactivate Issue

  IS -> IS : saveIssue(newIssue)
  IS --> IC : issueResult
  deactivate IS

  note over IS, Issue
  Creator / Information Expert:
  Project는 Issue collection을 소유하지 않는다.
  IssueService가 Project 존재/권한을 확인하고,
  Issue.create(...)가 priority 기본값 적용과 CREATED history 기록을 담당한다.
  프로젝트 관계는 Issue.projectId로 표현한다.
  end note

  IC --> User : issueRegistered(issueId,\nstatus=NEW,\nconfirmation)
end

opt Auth User wants to add an initial comment
  ref over User, IC
  UC2 Add Comment
  addComment(issueId, content)
  end ref
end

@enduml
